It is almost Christmas... I already got my biggest and most precious gifts: serenity, loved ones by my side, health and you all supporting what I/we do with @lacunacoilofficial .

This is what I wish for you all to get in these days (and in 2020 and forever) : happiness.
Material things are surely lots of fun but they are temporary, there is so much, much more...
Cherish what you have, enjoy every little thing, be positive.
Sometimes the smaller thing are the most important things in life. 
I want to wish a lot of strenght to the ones who are going through a dark period right now, I know it is hard and you feel like everything around you is hopeless but I PROMISE it will get better, try to get the best memories out of every moment and every person around you üñ§

Merry Christmas/Christless/Holiday/Hanukkah or anything you might be celebrating.

Love you all immensely! (Pic by one of my most precious -and √ºber talented-  friends @jeremysaffer )
